Package: coorsim
Type: Package
Title: Detects Coordinated Posting Behavior Based on Co-Similarity
Version: 0.0.8
Date: 2026-06-28
Authors@R: 
    person("Thiele", "Daniel", email="daniel.thiele@fu-berlin.de", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: 'R' package for detection of coordinated posting behavior. Detects groups of social media accounts that post semantically similar content within short time frames, based on cosine similarities of post embeddings. 
    Provides a comprehensive set of functions to generate embeddings (via 'reticulate', 'uv'), to efficiently compute co-similarities (via 'RcppParallel'),
    to detect coordinated communites, automatically label communities with locally hosted LLMs (via 'rollama'), and to plot results.
